\f0\fs24 \cf2 <$Scr_Cs::2><!$Scr_Ps::1><$Scr_Ps::0>
\f2\b\fs32 Duplex Gauge
\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 <!$Scr_Cs::2>
\f1\fs32 :  This type features two separate bourdon tubes and pointers within a single gauge housing, allowing simultaneous measurement of two different pressures.  Useful for displaying two different but related pressures simultaneously, for example the inlet and outlet pressures on a heat exchanger.\
\pard\sb40\sa40\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

